headline: Sun Life Adjusts Fund Lineup And DentaQuest Leadership As Stock Screens Cheap
summary: Sun Life Financial (TSX:SLF) is changing sub-advisory roles on certain mutual funds, moving responsibilities from BlackRock to State Street. The company is also rebranding the affected mutual funds to reflect the new sub-advisory structure. Separately, Sun Life's DentaQuest business has appointed a new dental director for Texas. For a global insurer and asset manager like Sun Life Financial, shifts in mutual fund sub-advisory and branding relate directly to how it positions its investment...
